 { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e1a88769-af82-4362-9d40-8ddb96bdce58\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-abee4a82-a996-4837-baff-b9f2a98b48e1\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>소통</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-47d8a5c1-8cd2-402b-8cd1-d7f14ac628ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 중요한 (주)파파스컴퍼니에서는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c72ed096-8cfe-4c9b-85a5-b987d5ba8e76\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-860395ca-5b21-40e7-a8b5-f5c3fe2bc04d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">컨펌과 결재가 완료되면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-371993cc-83c9-4f90-8306-d83e58c97617\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-131a5977-e8af-45c5-adf8-25970fd350b9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품 수령과 디자인 작업에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-29b765e5-6151-4acd-9c3f-d1b31a142414\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2621bbf-cf77-4e19-8af3-8507e9b89673\" style=\"color:#555555;\">착수합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-463071bc-8f97-4626-bfcc-f827632bfd62\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-773200a0-d643-4e09-a3d2-fb75a78afe95\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-48f14ae8-cafc-4e8a-b135-70f025b3ea7b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb676c25-38be-428d-b461-55c857e673a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이후의 진행 상황은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f5094254-af96-46bb-b8b0-c2188503f04b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-269fa528-5b13-4961-b6ef-e94a8a7bf7bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객과 소통하면서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e084f4bb-ed36-463d-b763-9fe10fb6cec6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f9270758-1b8a-49bc-a9f6-2233052bd397\" style=\"color:#555555;\">실제 보고되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cc09cada-abc9-4ee7-ad41-dfde7d51994d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4c49100-f6ee-4168-ab18-cc362c89d5cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8fd3407a-1a61-4128-9bf0-c8927ddef61c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c682c215-ceb6-4e0e-8bd5-5e847aa4fc2c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div clas